{"tid":1305892,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"「港大研究生召集」星期日14/7一齊番HKU投票（附懶人包）","createTime":"2019-07-11T03:26:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T04:39:12.000Z","uid":9053,"like":52,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"0e6352756a0540ad637f2591fe19b6486e275b52","tid":1305892,"uid":9053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:26:35.000Z","msg":"香港大學研究生會（PGSA)，之前<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">動議將繁體撇出官方語言，以及引入強調維持社會秩序條文</span></span><br />\n<br />\n第一次修改出左之後，因為條文有問題，同埋時間太短（一星期），俾人屌到飛天<br />\n第二次大會今個星期日搞，有票嘅人一定要出席去履行會員義務<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">日期：周日（7月14日）<br />\n時間：下午2點開始周年大會<br />\n地點：研究生堂王賡武講堂<br />\n謹記：帶有效學生證</span></span><br />\n<br />\nPGSA動議內容如下<br />\n<br />\n動議一：<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">更改官方語言</span><br />\n<br />\n原文（2017年）<br />\nArticle 3 &ndash; OFFICIAL LANGUAGES<br />\na) English and Chinese shall be the official languages of the Association;<br />\nb) For Chinese, traditional Chinese shall be used in writing.<br />\nc) Documents can only be written and explained by English.<br />\n<br />\n第一次修改：<br />\nEnglish and Chinese shall be the official languages of the Association.<br />\nOfficial documents, regulations, and resolutions shall have a version in English.<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">冇左繁體中文</span></span><br />\n<br />\n俾人屌完，第二次修改：<br />\n加入<br />\n&quot;For Chinese, in its writing form shall mean traditional Chinese.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n動議二：<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">加入警署社團註冊及遵守香港現行法律條文</span><br />\n<br />\n原文（2017年）<br />\n無相關條文<br />\n<br />\n第一次修改<br />\n加入<br />\nArticle 6&mdash;LEGALITY<br />\nThe Association is registered as a society at Hong Kong Police Force.<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">The Association and all the activities shall not violate the Basic Law</span> of the Hong Kong Special Administrative Region (HKSAR) of the People&rsquo;s Republic of China, other laws of HKSAR, <span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">public order and good customs.</span></span><br />\n<br />\n俾人屌完，第二次修改：<br />\n刪除有關條文<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果你係睇唔過眼嘅，麻煩一齊加入</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HUu1MWq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHUu1MWq.png&h=06e682fa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9c3dfae89bdb3224db217cdf3694967842336b1c","tid":1305892,"uid":9053,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:28:17.000Z","msg":"我有野講"},{"pid":"49a24f791fb6fdd4e5ce70c769b47f86b8315747","tid":1305892,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:28:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BKMofAK.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBKMofAK.gif&h=caf841ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d85343a603c69d4c90fdb6fc383074015cb0835b","tid":1305892,"uid":9053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:28:42.000Z","msg":"我有票投"},{"pid":"ffd9f0cd64020ef35d4ccb095bcc9a3ca12000d3","tid":1305892,"uid":9053,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:28:58.000Z","msg":"我有野講<br />\n我有票投"},{"pid":"1c4c3229b7674c29c21e7618e9c7ae84df420891","tid":1305892,"uid":9053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:29:17.000Z","msg":"我有野講<br />\n我有票投"},{"pid":"345fb001dd8f8fe417af97f8dcd501fc3200863a","tid":1305892,"uid":9053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:29:56.000Z","msg":"我有野講<br />\n我有票投"},{"pid":"77317ccee5566c58d8616c855ce098eaa421549d","tid":1305892,"uid":9053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:30:23.000Z","msg":"我有野講<br />\n我有票投"},{"pid":"efc38d5ddf3d1dbf2ee3aa253dfe627a36ecaf31","tid":1305892,"uid":263367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-0